init_power_intent_file(25.10)                    init_power_intent_file(25.10)

Name
       init_power_intent_file

Syntax
        init_power_intent_file <file_name>

       Type: String

       Default: ""

       Specifies  the  power  intent file, which supports the UPF 1801 and CPF
       format. This is a read-only global  variable.  The  power  intent  file
       specified  by  this  global  variable are read by the read_power_intent
       command.

Related Information
       read_power_intent

